titleStmt.title: A list of the names of the judges of the High Court of Justice, for tryall of the King appointed by an act of the Commons in England in Parliament assembled. And a list of the officers of the said court, by them elected.

notesStmt.note: Annotation on Thomason copy: in the name 'Colonell Harbottle Morley' the 'tle' has been underlined and the word "Herbort" [or "Herbert"] written along side; at foot of page: "Jan: 11th 1648"; the 9 in imprint date has been crossed through.
Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
